  "aboutTitle": "About the Project",
  "aboutMissionMd": "# ColdBit Wallet Mission\n\nThis application was forged with an absolute purpose: **Assume that all internet environments are compromised or inherently hostile**.\n\n## Design Principles\n1. **Pure Air-gapped**: \n   Your device will not send a single private key to the open internet. Only PSBT signing.\n2. **RAM Layer Defense (MemGuard)**: \n   Seeds (Seed Phrases) exist in temporary sealed cryptographic RAM. Pulsed and burned at discretion.\n\n---\n\n### Implemented Security Components:\n- **libsodium**: Argon2id style hashing derivation and isolated storage.\n- **Fail-Close Policy**: Any disturbance (exiting the App, biometric failure, detected jailbreak) collapses the session by protocol.\n\n*The software is for sovereign use. Verify the Code Hash and build it yourself.*",

